{"tid":1182734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六四學運領袖封從德遭入境處原機遣返","createTime":"2019-06-02T11:47:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T20:45:23.000Z","uid":249885,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7f7c7268f8b4b3c65664706e964293608318dc04","tid":1182734,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T11:47:43.000Z","msg":"香港支聯會副主席蔡耀昌今天傍晚證實，下午1時抵達香港機場即被帶走的「六四」學運領袖封從德，已被相關單位裁定遣返出發地，未能入境香港。據報導，封從德是由日本東京搭機前往香港。<br />\n<br />\n綜合港媒報導，封從是受香港支聯會邀請前往，準備參加6月4日晚間在維園舉辦的「六四」30週年紀念晚會。<br />\n<br />\n過埋逃犯條例俾人送支國審都唔定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780877d1ad56c5ecff3d30331f88ad07df8fbb2d","tid":1182734,"uid":15646,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T11:50:55.000Z","msg":"【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道"},{"pid":"63240496a7cf20bafac222346a5b66f5d60d121f","tid":1182734,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T12:11:38.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4dc2876467a240d42a40b0934c2979fc63171aee","tid":1182734,"uid":2054,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T12:25:39.000Z","msg":"入境處曲線炒熱69示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840aec1ec6ff1ce25b32f7761ace3cd094a42c85","tid":1182734,"uid":138427,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T12:32:11.000Z","msg":"睇完之後真係同中國冇分別....睇唔到香港前景...."},{"pid":"c6db52cc310b2b2664909754101f5b582119d401","tid":1182734,"uid":89045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:05:15.000Z","msg":"黑境"},{"pid":"233ee92dd04c67abe6edcdf14acc0d47de64bcea","tid":1182734,"uid":234695,"like":9,"dislike":0